Here's a PlantUML sequence diagram representing the deployment behavior of the ESP8266 Weather Station system:

```plantuml
@startuml zoolhelmy_ESP8266-Weather-Station

participant "ESP8266\nNodeMCU" as ESP
participant "Sensors" as Sensors
participant "ThingSpeak" as TS
participant "OpenWRT\nRouter" as Router
participant "GitHub\nRepository" as GitHub

activate ESP
ESP -> Sensors : Read sensor data
activate Sensors
Sensors --> ESP : Return sensor readings
deactivate Sensors

ESP -> TS : Publish data via MQTT
activate TS
TS --> ESP : Acknowledge
deactivate TS

ESP -> Router : Publish data via MQTT
activate Router
Router --> ESP : Acknowledge
deactivate Router

loop Every day
    Router -> Router : Generate graphs from RRDTool data
    Router -> GitHub : Push updated graphs
    activate GitHub
    GitHub --> Router : Confirm push
    deactivate GitHub
end

ESP -> ESP : Start local HTTP server
activate ESP

@enduml
```